": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2070355591030050973", "text": "Most of the oil leaving Hormuz is Iranian, writes @anasalhajji \n\nMost of it is headed to China.\n\nMeanwhile, Saudi &amp; UAE tankers reportedly turned back today.\n\nThis is a one-sided opening where Iran gets what it wants &amp; others turn around\n\n#OOTT #Oil #Hormuz #Iran #China https://t.co/4pXhCK4y", "time": "03:56", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 20243, "likes": 276, "replies": 13, "retweets": 58, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 22, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2070396326445973603", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2070396326445973603", "text": "PHOTOS OF THE DAY: Saudi Arabia is loading simultaneously 4 supertankers in the Persian Gulf. Two started loading yesterday at the single-point moorings of Ju’aymah (see post below) with their AIS visible (and a 3rd is waiting nearby). This morning, two others appear to be loading at Ras Tanura's Se", "time": "06:38", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 269992, "likes": 583, "replies": 20, "retweets": 104, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 71, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2070417577587671459", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2070417577587671459", "text": "Filed under \"least surprising news\" category: \n\nChina is leaving room for coal consumption to grow in coming years. “We will always prioritize energy security,” Wang Hongzhi, head of the National Energy Administration, said on Friday.\n\nhttps://t.co/W0NPmILaM0", "time": "08:03", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 34260, "likes": 199, "replies": 15, "retweets": 71, "quotes": 8, "bookmarks": 27, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["China demand"]}}, {"id": "2070436136766341562", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2070436136766341562", "text": "Saudi Aramco resumed crude loadings at Ras Tanura on Friday after a nearly four-month stop with at least two Bahri VLCCs loading (~2 mbbl each) and another waiting, signaling a restart of exports from the Gulf #OOTT", "time": "09:16", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 37970, "likes": 211, "replies": 6, "retweets": 52, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 16, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "OPEC+"]}}, {"id": "2070469283130327392", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2070469283130327392", "text": "Middlemen offer Iranian oil to Indian refiners after US waiver, sources say\n#oott https://t.co/d7Qme3XUYC", "time": "11:28", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 16037, "likes": 29, "replies": 0, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "China demand"]}}, {"id": "2070518035505459646", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2070518035505459646", "text": "Iraq's Oil Ministry: OPEC Has Begun Gradually Restoring Iraq’s Pre-War Production Allocations Which Will Strengthen Production Capacity And Support Oil Sector Recovery #OOTT", "time": "14:42", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 16456, "likes": 7, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2070520353420399079", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2070520353420399079", "text": "#OOTT | Oman Reportedly European Warned Allies Sh